  • Packages that use com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.enablement.configuration 
    Package Description
    com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.enablement
    The com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.enablement package provides interfaces to manage enablement of the feature that allows to collectively manage hosts within the cluster with a single software specification.
    com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.enablement.configuration
    The com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.enablement.configuration package provides interfaces to manage enablement of configuration on an ESX cluster.
